  "description": "A vibrant nighttime scene featuring a cityscape illuminated with lights, including a prominent suspension bridge and a fireworks display. The foreground showcases a modern, illuminated bridge extending towards a city skyline. Buildings of varying heights are visible, adorned with numerous lights, creating a dazzling effect. In the distance, fireworks explode in bursts of red, pink, and white, adding a dynamic element to the scene. The background reveals rolling hills and a dark sky providing contrast to the bright lights. The overall view is a wide-angle shot capturing the expansive urban landscape.",
